  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "4b36720db3:3",
      "text": "这样不仅可能获得更好的 reference photos，也能得到 material 本身的“feel”。",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4b36720db3:4",
      "text": "Feel your materials（通过触摸理解材质表面特性）",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4b36720db3:6",
      "text": "它是 smooth 还是 rough？如果 rough，到底有多 rough？",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4b36720db3:7",
      "text": "我会仔细观察 bump。它是 fine 还是 large？是 sharp 还是 smooth？",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4b36720db3:12",
      "text": "你可以拍摄很多类型的 photographs，从 albedo textures，到 dust、scratches、smudges、streaks 和 drips 都可以。",
      "ascii_letters": 57,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4b36720db3:13",
      "text": "如果你拍摄的是 diffuse textures，通常会希望它们是 tileable 的，然后再把 textures 手绘到 asset 上。",
      "ascii_letters": 36,
      "cjk_chars": 24
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4b36720db3:14",
      "text": "当你拍摄用于 grunge map 的照片时，通常会希望它是 black and white，以便用作 hand-painted layer masks。",
      "ascii_letters": 43,
      "cjk_chars": 21
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4b36720db3:15",
      "text": "The Foundry 有一场很棒的 live session，Stuart Ashley 在其中讲解如何 capture materials，内容从 14.30 开始。",
      "ascii_letters": 49,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4b36720db3:16",
      "text": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yt1IRe_pnRQ",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    }
